        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How does Verg work?</h3>
            <p>Verg is a journaling app designed to help you write on paper. Start the timer, set your phone down, and write with pen and paper while the candle burns. When you're done, take a photo of your page to track your progress.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I restore my purchases?</h3>
            <p>Go to Settings in the app and tap "Restore Purchases". Make sure you're signed in with the same Apple ID you used for the original purchase.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Why can't I access the camera?</h3>
            <p>Verg needs camera permission to capture photos of your journal pages. Go to your device's Settings > Verg and enable Camera access.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I cancel my subscription?</h3>
            <p>Subscriptions are managed through Apple. Go to Settings > [Your Name] > Subscriptions on your device to manage or cancel your Verg subscription.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is my data private?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Your journal photos are stored locally on your device. We do not have access to your writing or photos.</p>
        </div>

